to block the video?

47:43.611 --> 47:45.154
Well, we might be able
to block some sites,

47:45.237 --> 47:48.115
- but if they have enough mirrors...
- Don't block anything.

47:48.198 --> 47:49.492
Yes, sir.

47:52.119 --> 47:54.038
The whole world should watch this.

47:54.955 --> 47:56.457
And we should, too.

48:03.548 --> 48:07.802
- What you said, "We're at war..."
- I want to build a coalition.

48:07.885 --> 48:09.554
- More air strikes?
- Ground, air...

48:09.637 --> 48:11.263
The full force of our military.

48:11.346 --> 48:13.933
Well, I wish you would have
consulted first.

48:14.016 --> 48:17.520
- This type of escalation...
- Not escalation, Cathy. Obliteration.

48:19.396 --> 48:21.649
This is
your response to the article?

48:22.567 --> 48:24.109
We're doing what's necessary.

48:30.575 --> 48:34.411
When you find them...
