50:38.493 --> 50:39.912
No.

50:52.758 --> 50:55.260
Have you ever watched someone die?

51:13.070 --> 51:15.530
I know you gotta go
back there tonight...

51:16.448 --> 51:17.992
but when you're done...

51:18.909 --> 51:20.577
whenever that is...

